oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ray Lambrecht Job No. 36811
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Wells, Kitty; Jones, Grandpa, 1913-1998;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 1370) for an order placed by Ray Lambrecht for 200 two color jumbos for a performance by Kitty Wells and Grandpa Jones at the Memorial Auditorium in Sterling, Colorado on June 15. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
